Class GPML2021FormatAbstract

java.lang.Object
org.pathvisio.libgpml.model.GPMLFormatAbstract
org.pathvisio.libgpml.model.GPML2021FormatAbstract
Direct Known Subclasses:
GPML2021Reader, GPML2021Writer
public abstract class GPML2021FormatAbstract
extends GPMLFormatAbstract
Read / write GPML files. Base implementation for different GpmlFormat versions. Code that is shared between multiple versions is located here.
